* The data pattern needs to be (P=PATTERN, C=COLOR, S=Sound):
* 1		S
* 192	PPPPS	first 1/3rd, chars 0-95
* 1		S
* 192	CCCCS
* 1		S
* 192	PPPPS	second 1/3rd, chars 0-95
* 1		S
* 192	CCCCS
* 1		S
* 192	PPPPS	second 1/3rd, chars 96-191
* 1		S
* 192	CCCCS
* 1		S
* 192	PPPPS	third 1/3rd, chars 0-95
* 1		S
* 192	CCCCS
